# assets-images.mdc
## Image & Asset Management Standards

THIS FILE DEFINES HOW TO HANDLE IMAGES AND STATIC ASSETS.
Following these rules ensures performance, SEO, and consistency.

---

## Directory Structure

```
project/
├── public/
│   ├── images/
│   │   ├── hero/           # Hero/banner images
│   │   ├── team/           # Team member photos
│   │   ├── locations/      # Location photos
│   │   ├── services/       # Service-related images
│   │   ├── icons/          # Static icons (if not using icon library)
│   │   └── og/             # Open Graph images
│   ├── fonts/              # Custom font files
│   ├── favicon.ico
│   ├── apple-touch-icon.png
│   ├── robots.txt
│   └── sitemap.xml
├── src/
│   └── assets/             # Assets that need processing (rare)
```

