## Image Naming Conventions

### Format

```
[category]-[description]-[variant].[extension]
```

### Examples

| Good | Bad |
|------|-----|
| `hero-homepage-desktop.webp` | `IMG_1234.jpg` |
| `team-jane-smith.webp` | `photo1.png` |
| `location-garden-city-exterior.webp` | `gc.jpg` |
| `service-massage-therapy.webp` | `massage.jpeg` |
| `og-homepage.jpg` | `og.jpg` |

### Rules

- Lowercase only
- Hyphens between words (not underscores or spaces)
- Descriptive names (SEO benefit)
- Include size/variant if multiple versions exist
- No special characters

