## Image Sizes

### Size Guidelines

| Image Type | Max Width | Max File Size | Aspect Ratio |
|------------|-----------|---------------|--------------|
| Hero images | 1920px | 200KB | 16:9 or custom |
| Content images | 1200px | 150KB | Varies |
| Thumbnails | 400px | 30KB | 1:1 or 4:3 |
| Team photos | 600px | 50KB | 1:1 or 3:4 |
| OG images | 1200px | 100KB | 1.91:1 (1200x630) |
| Icons | 64px | 5KB | 1:1 |

### Responsive Images

Use `srcset` for responsive images (Next.js handles this automatically):

```tsx
<Image
  src="/images/hero/homepage.jpg"
  alt="Homepage hero"
  fill
  sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 50vw, 33vw"
/>
```

