## Image Optimization

### Before Adding Images

1. **Resize** to maximum needed dimensions
2. **Compress** using tools like:
   - Squoosh (squoosh.app)
   - TinyPNG (tinypng.com)
   - ImageOptim (Mac)
3. **Convert** to WebP when possible
4. **Name** according to conventions

### Optimization Targets

| Metric | Target |
|--------|--------|
| Hero image | < 200KB |
| Content image | < 150KB |
| Thumbnail | < 30KB |
| Total page images | < 1MB |

