## Alt Text Requirements

### Every Image MUST Have Alt Text

```tsx
// CORRECT
<Image src="/team/jane-smith.webp" alt="Jane Smith, Licensed Clinical Psychologist" />

// CORRECT (decorative)
<Image src="/decorative-pattern.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />

// WRONG
<Image src="/team/jane-smith.webp" />
<Image src="/team/jane-smith.webp" alt="image" />
<Image src="/team/jane-smith.webp" alt="photo" />
```

### Alt Text Guidelines

| Image Type | Alt Text Should Include |
|------------|------------------------|
| Team photo | Name, title/credentials |
| Location | Location name, what's shown |
| Service | Service name, context |
| Hero | Key message or description |
| Decorative | Empty string (`alt=""`) |

### SEO-Friendly Alt Text

```tsx
// Good - descriptive and includes keywords naturally
alt="Individual therapy session at [Business Name] [Location] office"

// Bad - keyword stuffing
alt="keyword keyword keyword keyword location state"

// Bad - not descriptive
alt="therapy"
```

