## Placeholder Strategy (Development)

### During Development

When images aren't available yet, use consistent placeholders:

```tsx
// Option 1: CSS placeholder
<div className="aspect-video bg-[rgb(var(--color-placeholder))] rounded-lg" />

// Option 2: Placeholder image service
<Image 
  src="https://placehold.co/1200x630/E6E4E0/01153D?text=Hero+Image"
  alt="Placeholder for hero image"
  width={1200}
  height={630}
/>

// Option 3: Local placeholder
<Image 
  src="/images/placeholder.svg"
  alt="Image coming soon"
  width={1200}
  height={630}
/>
```

### Placeholder Styling

```css
.img-placeholder {
  background: rgb(var(--color-placeholder));
  border: 1px dashed rgb(var(--border));
}

/* On dark backgrounds */
.bg-navy .img-placeholder {
  background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.1);
  border-color: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.2);
}
```

