## Open Graph Images

### Requirements

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Size | 1200 x 630 pixels |
| Format | JPEG or PNG |
| Max file size | 100KB |
| Location | `/public/images/og/` |

### Per-Page OG Images

```
/public/images/og/
├── og-homepage.jpg
├── og-about.jpg
├── og-services.jpg
├── og-contact.jpg
└── og-default.jpg  # Fallback
```

### Implementation

```tsx
// In page metadata
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  openGraph: {
    images: [{
      url: '/images/og/og-about.jpg',
      width: 1200,
      height: 630,
      alt: 'About [Business Name]',
    }],
  },
}
```

