## Font Files

### Location

```
/public/fonts/
├── CustomFont-Regular.woff2
├── CustomFont-SemiBold.woff2
└── CustomFont-Regular.otf  # Fallback
```

### Format Priority

1. WOFF2 (best compression, wide support)
2. WOFF (older browser fallback)
3. OTF/TTF (last resort)

### Loading

```tsx
// In layout.tsx
import localFont from 'next/font/local'

const customFont = localFont({
  src: [
    {
      path: '../../public/fonts/CustomFont-Regular.woff2',
      weight: '400',
      style: 'normal',
    },
    {
      path: '../../public/fonts/CustomFont-SemiBold.woff2',
      weight: '600',
      style: 'normal',
    },
  ],
  display: 'swap',
  variable: '--font-custom',
})
```

