## SVG Icons

### Inline vs File

| Use | Method |
|-----|--------|
| Icons that change color | Inline SVG or icon library |
| Static decorative graphics | SVG file |
| Logos | SVG file |

### Icon Libraries (Preferred)

```tsx
// Using Lucide React (recommended)
import { Phone, Mail, MapPin } from 'lucide-react'

<Phone className="h-5 w-5 text-green" />
```

### Inline SVG

```tsx
// For custom icons
<svg 
  className="h-6 w-6" 
  fill="none" 
  viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
  stroke="currentColor"
  aria-hidden="true"
>
  <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="..." />
</svg>
```

