## Performance Checklist

### Before Deployment

- [ ] All images optimized (< target file sizes)
- [ ] All images have alt text
- [ ] Hero images use `priority` prop
- [ ] Below-fold images lazy load (default in Next.js)
- [ ] Images have explicit width/height (prevents CLS)
- [ ] OG images exist for all key pages
- [ ] Favicon configured correctly
- [ ] No broken image links

### Lighthouse Targets

| Metric | Target |
|--------|--------|
| Largest Contentful Paint | < 2.5s |
| Cumulative Layout Shift | < 0.1 |
| Image optimization | No warnings |

