## FORBIDDEN

- Images without alt text (except decorative with `alt=""`)
- Unoptimized images (> 500KB)
- Using `<img>` instead of Next.js `<Image>` component
- Hardcoded image dimensions that don't match actual size
- Missing width/height causing layout shift
- PNG for photos (use WebP/JPEG)
- JPEG for graphics with transparency
- Generic filenames (IMG_1234.jpg, photo.png)

